snippet.title: Pahalgam Attack | Pahalgam Hero Who Carried Injured Boy On His Back: 'Humanity Before Religion'
snippet.description:
The massive terror attack in Pahalgam, Jammu and Kashmir, while spreading shock and horror, also showed hope as multiple heroes stepped forward from among the locals. One such was Sajad Ahmed Bhatt. A video of him carrying a boy, injured when the terrorists opened fire on a group of tourists, killing 26 people, has been widely circulated. The video shows Mr Bhatt running downhill over the rocky terrain, his steps never faltering. The boy was on his back, clad in Mr Bhatt's orange jacket to keep him warm.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Barcelona 3-2 Real Madrid | Copa del Rey Final 2025
snippet.description:
Real Madrid were defeated in extra time in the final of the Copa del Rey. In a strong second half, Madrid came back from Pedri's goal in the 28th minute with a free-kick from Mbappé in the 70th minute and a header from Tchouameni seven minutes later. In the 84th minute, Ferran Torres scored to take the game into extra time, which was decided by Koundé in the 116th minute with a shot from the edge of the area.

es.title: RESUMEN | Barcelona 3-2 Real Madrid | Final de la Copa del Rey 2025
es.description:
Derrota en la prórroga de la final de la Copa del Rey. El Real Madrid, en una gran segunda mitad, dio la vuelta al tanto de Pedri en el 28’ con un lanzamiento de falta de Mbappé en el 70’ y un cabezazo de Tchouameni siete minutos más tarde. En el 84’ marcó Ferran Torres y llevó el encuentro a la prórroga, que decidió Koundé en el 116’ con un disparo desde la frontal.

snippet.title: Phulera Ka Panchayati Raj | Alhua Vikas ft. Neena Gupta, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Durgesh Kumar
snippet.description:
Phulera mein banne wala hain Bhandaar Ghar par kya har baar ki tarah iss baar bhi Banrakas ko hogi Pradhan ji ke iss kaam se dikkat? Ab Phulera mein hoga vikas ya Banrakas ek baar phir kahega alhua vikas? Jaanne ke liye Rashtriya Panchayati Raj Diwas par dekhiye Phulera Ka Panchayati Raj.

#TVF #Phulera #PanchayatiRaj 

Watch all parts of #PhuleraKaPanchayatiRaj here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTB0eCoUXErY5Jgt1VEjySYTaPde_w5oG&si=pwoMUSOFjMWWbkHS

This film, released on the occasion of National Panchayati Raj Day (राष्ट्रीय पंचायती राज दिवस; 24th April, 2025), highlights the importance of Own Sources of Revenue (OSR) in enabling Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) to become self-reliant and better equipped to take up development works on their own.  It encourages Panchayats to adopt simple and effective ways to raise awareness among citizens about timely payment of Property Tax and other local taxes. These contributions directly support better service delivery, creation of public assets, and overall village development – making citizens active partners in the progress of their communities.  With the central message “जमा करके कर, बनाईये अपनी पंचायत को आत्मनिर्भर”, the film inspires collective efforts towards strengthening grassroots governance. The Ministry of Panchayati Raj remains committed to promoting OSR enhancement as a means to deepen decentralization and participatory rural development.

The Ministry of Panchayati Raj (MoPR), Government of India, is responsible for overseeing all matters related to Panchayati Raj and Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) across the country. MoPR plays a pivotal role in promoting the decentralization process and strengthening rural local governance in States and Union Territories. For more information, visit the Ministry's official website: https://panchayat.gov.in

snippet.title: ভাৰতে বন্ধ কৰিলে দিলে সিন্ধু নদীৰ পানী। কম্পন উঠিছে পাকিস্তানৰ সদনত।
snippet.description: ভাৰতে বন্ধ কৰিলে দিলে সিন্ধু নদীৰ পানী। কম্পন উঠিছে পাকিস্তানৰ সদনত। ২০ কোটি পাকিস্তানীয়ে পানী নাপায় কৰিছে হাহাকাৰ। ইয়াৰ মাজতে জম্মু-কাশ্মীৰত উপস্থিত সেনা প্ৰধান ।পৰিস্থিতিৰ বুজ লৈছে সেনা প্ৰধানে। কম্পিত পাকিস্তান।

snippet.title: Adulting | S3E02 - Rat-Trap | Ft. Aisha & Yashaswini | Dice Media | Web Series
snippet.description:
Ray is reeling from disappointment after losing the project lead opportunity at work — and to make it worse, it went to the new guy, Abhinav. Struggling to focus, keep up with deadlines, and stay emotionally afloat, she starts to question her worth at the office.

Meanwhile, Nikhat is on a mission of her own: to finally make a move on Abeer. With Manav’s less-than-helpful guidance, things go sideways fast — and hilariously. From romantic misfires to workplace pressure, Adulting Season 3 continues to explore the chaos of ambition, heartbreak, and growing pains in your 20s.

Starring Aisha Ahmed, Yashaswini Dayama, Viraj Ghelani, and Rohan Khurana, Episode 2 brings more warmth, awkward laughs, and too-real emotions as Ray and Nikhat juggle friendship, failure, and flirtations — all while trying to keep it together in the middle of Mumbai.

localized.title: Adulting | S3E02 - Rat-Trap | Ft. Aisha & Yashaswini | Dice Media | Web Series
localized.description:
Ray is reeling from disappointment after losing the project lead opportunity at work — and to make it worse, it went to the new guy, Abhinav. Struggling to focus, keep up with deadlines, and stay emotionally afloat, she starts to question her worth at the office.

Meanwhile, Nikhat is on a mission of her own: to finally make a move on Abeer. With Manav’s less-than-helpful guidance, things go sideways fast — and hilariously. From romantic misfires to workplace pressure, Adulting Season 3 continues to explore the chaos of ambition, heartbreak, and growing pains in your 20s.

Starring Aisha Ahmed, Yashaswini Dayama, Viraj Ghelani, and Rohan Khurana, Episode 2 brings more warmth, awkward laughs, and too-real emotions as Ray and Nikhat juggle friendship, failure, and flirtations — all while trying to keep it together in the middle of Mumbai.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 28 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Diamond Paints - Ujooba Beauty Cream & Nestle Lactogrow - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 26th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang Digitally Presented by Diamond Paints - Ujooba Beauty Cream & Nestle Lactogrow

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.title: Chor Bazari Phir Se | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar, Wamiqa | Tanishk, Pritam, Irshad, Neeraj, Sunidhi
snippet.description:
Chor bazaari do nainon kee,
Pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi!

Presenting the highly awaited ‘Chor Bazari Phir Se’ from ‘Bhool Chuk Maaf’, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Wamiqa Gabbi! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Pritam, it is sung by Neeraj Shridhar, Sunidhi Chauhan, Zahrah S Khan and Tanishk Bagchi. Penned by Irshad Kamil, it is perfect for all the Bollywood nostalgia lovers and those who love a good beat to dance on. Play it on loop, add it to your playlists, and get your groove on with ‘Chor Bazari Phir Se’!

#ChorBazari #PhirSe #RajkummarRao #WamiqaGabbi #TanishkBagchi #Pritam #IrshadKamil #NeerajShridhar #SunidhiChauhan #ZahrahSKhan #BhoolChukMaaf 

Title: Chor Bazari Phir Se
Singer: Neeraj Shridhar, Sunidhi Chauhan, Zahrah S Khan and Tanishk Bagchi 
Composers: Tanishk Bagchi and Pritam 
Music Production: Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil
Language: Hindi
Mix Master: Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai
Original Music: Pritam
Director of Photography- Manu Anand
Director of Choreography- Vijay A Ganguly 
Costume Designer - Sheetal Iqbal Sharma 

Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast - Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan 
Directed By: Karan Sharma 
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota 
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi 
Background Score: Ketan Sodha 
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma 
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee 
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil
Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
Associate Producer: Vineeta S Tanwar

Lyrics:
Chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi 
Pyaar kee jo teri-meri umr aayi thi vo katt gayi
Tu bhi tu hai main bhi main hoon duniyaan saaree dekh ulat gayi
Tu naa jaane main naa jaanoon kaise saaree baath palat gayi
Ghatni hi thi ye bhi ghatana ghatate-ghatate lo ye ghat gai
Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi

Jhoomariya jhoomariya manwa
Ban baagi sa
Jhoomariya jhoomariya tanwa
Bedaagi
Man mera dhad dhad dhad dhadkaaye
Koi na phir sar sar sar chadh jaaye
Kasam se baazi haath na apne aaye
Nain agar lad jaayein

Taareef teri karnaa tuje khone se darana
Haan bhool gaya ab tujh pe din mein chaar dafa maranaa

Taareef teri karnaa tuje khone se darana
Haan bhool gaya ab tujh pe din mein chaar dafa maranaa

Laaj-sharam kee choti-moti jo thi dori vo bhi katt gayi
Chowk-chaubaare gali-mohalle khol ke main saare ghunghat gayi
Ek hue the do se donon donon kee ab raahen bant gayi
Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi

Bade hi nain ladaake se
Lade the roz baazaaron mein
Kisi ko dhoond hi lete the
Sadak pe roz hazaaron mein
Bahas nahin kam kam kam karte
Na ab yeh gham gham gham karte
Badal gaye dheere dheere do naina
Mera kya kya kya kehna

Haan chor bazaari do nainon kee pehle thi aadat jo hat gayi
Haan rang-birangaa paani pee ke sidhi-saadi kudi bighad gayi

लागे माथे के म मारे बंदा परे बगाके न 
जो अपने मन म एंडी हमने वेहे पेले है

 लाल र गैल्या धरया टूल म प्योर भाग का गोला रह स

are bheed paad daya bheed me badke fair guma dya sa

re ham apanee dhunen ma jeete, gelya saare baalak cheete jo maran maran na tayaar rahave vo tola rah sai 

mhaara thaade galiya rola rah sa 
cha kee galiya tola rah sa 
syaana gailya banti kaunaya 
dil maan baaba bhola rah sa

re ham kara jaabta rasiya ka samaan mangaake na 
laage maathe ke me maare banda pare baagaake na 
jo apane man ma endee hamne vohe pele sai 
are rehadee kaunaya lootee jhoothi dhons dikhke ne
re haande banake na ham kaal, aar donoo aankh rav se laal gelya dharya tool me pyor bhaag ka gola rah se

snippet.title: Day 4: Pakistan Big Drama! | Madan Gowri | Tamil | MG Squad 🖖🏻
snippet.description:
📧 For Brand Placements : madangowri@mcholas.com
________
📧 For Business and Interviews : madangowri@mcholas.com
-------------
In this Tamil video, Madan Gowri explains about the current situations between the Narendra Modi-led Indian government and Pakistan. He further breaks down the recent developments, including India’s response to the Pahalgam event, Pakistan’s official statement and the strategic implications of these actions. The video also covers international reactions, particularly from American President Donald Trump and China, as global powers closely monitor the evolving situation. Updates on the Indus Water Treaty, China’s stance on the Brahmaputra River, and the ongoing discussions in Balochistan between the BLA and Pakistan are explored. 

Madan Gowri explains India’s strategic moves clearly, helping viewers understand how these events are shaping the new geopolitical landscape of South Asia.
________

snippet.title: #PahalgamAttack | "காஷ்மிர் முஸ்லிம்கள் தான் காப்பாத்துனாங்க" | உயிர் தப்பிய தமிழர்கள் | Maalaimalar
snippet.description:
#PahalgamAttack | “காஷ்மீர் முஸ்லிம்கள் தான் எங்களை காப்பாத்தினாங்க” – உயிர் தப்பிய தமிழர்கள் உருக்கம் | Humanity in Crisis

🙏 Amid the horrifying Pahalgam terror attack, a group of Tamil tourists who narrowly escaped death, emotionally shared how local Kashmiri Muslims risked their lives to protect them. A powerful story of humanity rising above fear and violence.

💔 பஹல்காம் தாக்குதலில் உயிர் தப்பிய தமிழர்கள், “நம்மை காப்பாத்தினது காஷ்மீர்ல இருக்குற முஸ்லிம் மக்கள்தான்” என நெகிழ்ந்தனர்.
இது மதத்திற்கும், மொழிக்குமப்பாலும் மனிதநேயத்தின் உண்மையான வெளிப்பாடு.

#PahalgamAttack #KashmirMuslims #TamilTourists #HumanityFirst #BreakingNews #TamilNews #Maalaimalar #TerrorSurvivors #IndiaUnited #Tamilnews #MMNews #Maalaimalar 

For more videos, interviews, reviews & news, Subscribe here : http://bit.ly/2BFZApG

snippet.title: Pakistan Soldiers Retreat After Pahalgam Attack | ಭಾರತದ ಜೊತೆ ಯುದ್ಧಕ್ಕೆ ಪಾಕ್​​ ಸೈನಿಕರು ಹಿಂದೇಟು
snippet.description:
Pakistan Soldiers Retreat After Pahalgam Attack | ಭಾರತದ ಜೊತೆ ಯುದ್ಧಕ್ಕೆ ಪಾಕ್​​ ಸೈನಿಕರು ಹಿಂದೇಟು | Pahalgam Attack | INDIA vs Pakistan Military Comparison 2025 


Following India's strong vow to retaliate for the Pahalgam attack, Pakistan Soldiers Retreat After Pahalgam Attack as Pakistani soldiers have lost their fighting spirit despite large troop numbers. This major setback clearly shows that Pakistan Soldiers Retreat After Pahalgam Attack due to internal discontent and leadership failures, where even Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif’s orders are being ignored. The situation escalates further as Pakistan Soldiers Retreat After Pahalgam Attack, exposing the deep cracks within Pakistan’s military leadership. Stay tuned with TV5 Kannada for latest updates..!

ಭಾರತವನ್ನ ಕೆಣಕಿ ಕಂಗಾಲಾದ ‘ಪಾಪಿ’ಸ್ತಾನ, ಪಹಲ್ಗಾಮ್​​ ದಾಳಿಯ ಪ್ರತೀಕಾರಕ್ಕೆ ಇಂಡಿಯಾ ಶಪಥ., ಭಾರತದ ಜೊತೆ ಯುದ್ಧಕ್ಕೆ ಪಾಕ್​​ ಸೈನಿಕರು ಹಿಂದೇಟು.,  ಪಾಕ್​​ನಲ್ಲಿ ಸೈನ್ಯಕ್ಕೆ ಸಂಖ್ಯಾಬಲ ಇದ್ರೂ ಸಾಮರ್ಥ ಇಲ್ಲ, ಯುದ್ಧದ ಹುಮ್ಮಸ್ಸು ಕಳೆದುಕೊಂಡ ಪಾಕ್​ ಸೈನಿಕರು, ಪಾಕ್​ ಪ್ರಧಾನಿ ಶಬಬಾಜ್​ ಷರೀಫ್​​ ಮಾತು ಕೇಳದ ಸೈನಾಧಿಕಾರಿ,  ಯುದ್ಧಕ್ಕೆ ಪಾಕ್​ ಸೈನಿಕರ ಹಿಂದೇಟು..ಕಾರಣಗಳೇನು..?

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The director of Prey welcomes you to a world of hurt. Experience Predator: Badlands on the big screen, in theaters and IMAX November 7.
 
“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator (Schuster-Koloamatangi), outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Adulting | S3E01 - Pawri Ho Rahi Hai | Ft. Aisha & Yashaswini | Dice Media | Web Series
snippet.description:
Nikhat is back from Hyderabad and determined to make Ray’s 25th birthday unforgettable. Balloons, plans, surprises — she’s ready to go all out. But there’s just one problem: Ray doesn’t want to celebrate.

She’s got her eyes on something bigger — a life-changing project lead announcement at work the very next day. The last thing she wants is a hangover or distractions. But can birthdays be ignored? And more importantly, can best friends ever be on the same page when life pulls them in opposite directions?

Adulting Season 3 opens with all the emotional confusion, hilarious miscommunication, and ride-or-die friendship moments you’ve loved since Season 1. From navigating work anxiety to the pressure of turning 25, Episode 1 brings back the Mumbai madness, the career chaos, and the comfort of chosen family — one heartfelt moment at a time.

👭 Starring Aisha Ahmed and Yashaswini Dayama, & Viraj Ghelani, Adulting S3 dives deeper into the realities of millennial friendships, workplace hustle, and the little moments that define adulthood.

localized.title: Adulting | S3E01 - Pawri Ho Rahi Hai | Ft. Aisha & Yashaswini | Dice Media | Web Series
localized.description:
Nikhat is back from Hyderabad and determined to make Ray’s 25th birthday unforgettable. Balloons, plans, surprises — she’s ready to go all out. But there’s just one problem: Ray doesn’t want to celebrate.

She’s got her eyes on something bigger — a life-changing project lead announcement at work the very next day. The last thing she wants is a hangover or distractions. But can birthdays be ignored? And more importantly, can best friends ever be on the same page when life pulls them in opposite directions?

Adulting Season 3 opens with all the emotional confusion, hilarious miscommunication, and ride-or-die friendship moments you’ve loved since Season 1. From navigating work anxiety to the pressure of turning 25, Episode 1 brings back the Mumbai madness, the career chaos, and the comfort of chosen family — one heartfelt moment at a time.

👭 Starring Aisha Ahmed and Yashaswini Dayama, & Viraj Ghelani, Adulting S3 dives deeper into the realities of millennial friendships, workplace hustle, and the little moments that define adulthood.

snippet.title: Kashmir News: Jaipurরে সপ্তশক্তি কামান নিয়ে Rajasthan থর মরুভূমিতে পাক বর্ডারের কাছে War -প্রস্তুতি।
snippet.description:
ABP Ananda Live: প্রধানমন্ত্রীর বার্তার পর এবার প্রত্যাঘ্যাত ? রাজস্থানে যুদ্ধ-প্রস্তুতি ভারতীয় সেনার। ফের পাকিস্তানের বিরুদ্ধে সার্জিক্যাল স্ট্রাইক ? জয়পুরে সপ্তশক্তি কামান নিয়ে রাজস্থানের থর মরুভূমিতে পাক বর্ডারের কাছে যুদ্ধ-প্রস্তুতি। পাকিস্তানের সীমা অতিক্রম করে স্ট্রাইক ? এই যুদ্ধ-প্রস্তুতির মাধ্যমে।

snippet.title: பயங்கரவாதத்திற்கு எதிராக ஓங்கி ஒலிக்கும் முஸ்லிம் குரல்  Ghulam Nabi Azad|Pahalgam attack|Protest
snippet.description:
#Partnership ஜம்மு - காஷ்மீரின் பஹல்காமில் நடந்த பயங்கரவாத தாக்குதலை கண்டித்து, காஷ்மீர் மக்கள் தாமாக முன்வந்து போராடுவதை அம்மாநில முன்னாள் முதல்வர் குலாம் நபி ஆசாத் வரவேற்றுள்ளார்.

காஷ்மீர் மக்களின் உணர்வுகள் மீதான தாக்குதலை அவர்கள் ஒருபோதும் ஏற்பதில்லை. 

மதங்களை கடந்து மனிதத்துவத்தை போற்றும் காஷ்மீர் மக்களின் இந்த போராட்டம் மகத்தானது.

1989 - 90 காலகட்டத்தில் நான் காஷ்மீர் முதல்வராக கூட இல்லை. மகாராஷ்டிராவை சேர்ந்த எம்பியாக இருந்தேன்.#Ghulam Nabi Azad|Pahalgam attack|Protest
